Does stress cause hair loss ?






When the body is under a serious physical and emotional stress,
it is possible for the immune system to produce antibody and the antibody
attacks the hair follicles, which results in bald areas and spreads the hair
loss.








Is ArganRain approved by Ministry of Health ?






The statement has been made to Ministry of Health and
ArganRain is a product which have been approved by Ministry of Health.








By using ARGANRain, Is it possible for unmanageable hair to get softness and to be combed easy ?






As
ArganRain moisturizes hair, It allows hair to be combed easily and provides
softness.








What are the effects of argan oil on hair ?






Having rich vitamin E and fatty acids, Argan oil makes hair
strong, helping to prevent hair loss, giving hair silky lively looks and makes
hair easy to style.








Will it make me look younger?






Argan oil is well known for its anti-aging effects. It
includes a number of properties that support the production of collagen and
elastin and provide deep-penetrating moisturization, for firmer, more youthful
looking skin. It helps to erase fine lines, wrinkles, and crow's feet. Plus, it
includes potent antioxidants that fight free radical damage to help repair sun
damage and prevent premature aging








Won't this oil clog my pores and/or cause acne breakouts?






Argan oil doesn't clog your pores. In fact, it absorbs into
your skin quickly without making it feel greasy. And it contains a number of
anti-inflammatory, anti-bacterial, and healing properties that are actually
well known for fighting acne breakouts, healing blemishes, and even erasing
acne scars!








Are there any side effects?






No. It has been used topically for centuries with no
reported side effects.








Does ARGANRain help to prevent hair loss?






The formula of ArganRain has been prepared after long
studies against especially to stop hair loss.








Is ARGAN Rain effective against dandruff ?






ArganRain Special Formula helps to prevent the occuring
dandruff








Will Argan oil really eliminate my stretch marks?






Argan oil includes a number of properties that help to
smooth and diminish the appearance of stretch marks and scars from pregnancy,
weight loss, weight gain, growth spurts, and surgery.








Is ArganRain suitable for the dyed hair and hair with highlihts?






ArganRain products help the hair which has been damaged by
some chemical substances, environmental factors and hair dryer machine to look
healthy again








Is ARGANRain with argan oil very effective for hair growth ?






As Argan Rain nourishes hair from root to tip with very rich
ingredients and vitamins,it will make your hair grow faster.








What types of hair and skins are suitable for ARGANRain products ?






Our Argan Rain products are suitable for all types of hair
and skins on both females and males.








How do I use it as a nail strengthener?






Take one part argan oil and paint it directly on your nails
with a nail brush. Leave it for at least 15 minutes before rinsing off. For
cuticle softening, just massage the oil directly into your cuticles.








Are there any hazardous substances on human health in the products ?






ARGAN Rain products don't contain Sulfate, Slicone, Alcohol,
Salt and Dye. It is totally safe.








What tests have ARGAN Rain anti hair loss product passed successfully?






Our product has passed successfully microbiologically, dermatologically
and allergy-tested..








