Art Naturals, Argan Oil Shampoo, Hair Growth Treament, 16 fl oz (473 ml)


2


$25.99

























Product Overview










Description

 Argan Aloe Vera Green Tea Lavender  Helps Fight DHT Paraben Free Sulfate Free Professional Series For centuries, argan oil has been used to help strengthen and fortify the hair against damage. This treatment supercharges the benefits of argan oil with coenzyme Q10. Helping penetrate deeper thanks to nano particles, this soothing and effective treatment literally get to the rot of the problem.





Suggested Use


Shampoo hair with art naturals argan oil shampoo first. After rinsing, apply a generous amount of conditioner and comb trough hair. Wait two to three minutes while oils penetrate scalp and hair. Rinse and repeat as needed.






Other Ingredients

Water, aloe barbadensis (aloe) leaf juice, camellia sinensis (green tea) leaf, lamaniria (algae) extract, macrocystis pyrifera (sea kelp), aleurites moluccans (kukui) seed, lavandula angustifolia (lavender) flower, cocos nucifera (coconut) fruit, rosmarinus officinalis (rosemary), salvia officinalis leaf (sage) urtica dioica (nettle) leaf, euterpe oleracea (acai) fruit, arctium lappa root (burdock root), serenoa serrulata (saw  palmetto) fruit, prunus amygdalus dulcis (sweet almond) seed. zingiber officinale (ginger) root, capsicum annuum fruit, prunus serotina (wild cherry), bark, humulus lupulus (hops) cone, sesamum indicum (sesame) seed, citrus reticulata (tangerine) peel oil, pyrus malus (apple) fruit, yeast, ilex paraguariensis leaf extract, behentrimonium chloride, cetearyl alcohol, cetrimonium chloride, stearalkonium chloride, dicetyl-dimonium chloride, glyceryl stearate, fragrance, cetyl alcohol, hydroxyethyl cellulose, potassium olivoyl pca, glycerin, panthenol,, argania spinisa kernel oil, macadmia ternifolia seed oil, cocos nucifera (coconut) oil, hydrolyzed quinoa, phenoxyethanol, caprylyl glycol, tocopheryl acetate, magnesium ascorbyl phosphate, coenzyme Q10, apigenin, oleanolic acid, biotynol tripeptide-1, sorbic acid, benzyl alcohol, benzyl salicylate, disodiium edta, citric acid.





Warnings

For external use only. Avoid contact with eyes. Can cause eye irritation. In case of contact with eyes, rise thoroughly with water. If irritation occurs, discontinue and consult a physician.





