Additional Information

Details
Directions
Ingredients



Sulfate, Paraben and Gluten free
Provides intense shine						
Helps eliminate frizz


						Proclaim Argan Oil Hair Oil Treatment is uniquely formulated with Argan Oil and natural ingredients that condition, help repair dry, damage hair without weighing it down, eliminate frizz and infuse brilliant shine.					
					

						Apply a small amount of Proclaim Argan Oil Hair Oil Treatment in your palm and distribute evenly throughout damp or dry hair. Style as desired.					
					

						DIMETHICONE, CYCLOPENTASILOXANE, DIMETHICONOL, FRAGRANCE, C12-15 ALKYL BENZOATE, ARGANIA SPINOSA KERNEL OIL, OLEA EUROPAEA (OLIVE) FRUIT OIL, LINUM USITATISSIMUM (LINSEED) SEED OIL, YELLOW 11, RED 17, BUTYLPHENYL METHYLPROPIONAL, CITRONELLOL, COUMARIN, HEXYL CINNAMAL, LIMONENE, LINALOOL
					






