Nourishes & Conditions

Multi-Tasking Miracle Mascara

Luxurious, high-performance mascara provides a complete dose of intensive oil treatment for thicker, fuller, healthier looking lashes instantly!
Infused with 100% Pure Argan Oil, known as "liquid gold", this ultra-nourishing & conditioning formula adds lash shine and can build lash strength for less lash breakage.
Exotically scented mascara instantly volumizes & lengthens to create exotic, dramatic lashes!

 24 Hour Wear
High-performance, clump-free, smudge-free & flake-free formula provides 24 hour wear.
Moroccan Brush
Unique Moroccan inspired brush with rounded base creates luxurious volume while precise tip separates and defines even the smallest lashes.





Suggested Use


Directions: Sweep mascara brush from lash base to tips. Apply multiple coats for added volume.






Other Ingredients

Water, beeswax, iron oxides, copernicia cerifera (carnauba) wax, PVP, cyclopentasiloxane, glyceryl stearate, propylene glycol stearate SE, stearic acid, cyclohexasiloxane, triethanolamine, acrylates copolymer, argania spinosa (argan) kernel oil, cellulose, fragrance, oleic acid, phenoxyethanol, polybutene, PTFE, black 2, panthenol, tocopheryl acetate, styrene/acrylates copolymer, VP/hexadecene copolymer, cellulose gum, magnesium aluminum silicate, octyldodecanol, simethicone, tetrasodium EDTA.





